{"tid":536245,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的  最近畫畫畫得有點不開心","createTime":"2018-01-21T15:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T05:47:57.000Z","uid":136686,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"38fafda67d449146cfb5eb9a5b0766742782b148","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"最近畫畫畫得有點不開心<br />\n(其實已經不是最近,也許是一直以來)<br />\n<br />\n實際畫出來的東西<br />\n和想畫的東西總是有差別<br />\n<br />\n當這兩件事情差別不大,結果是可以接受的<br />\n也許可以用一些技法掩飾,透過調整已經畫了出來的東西盡量貼近自已心中想要的東西<br />\n甚至改變自已的心境,嘗試接受自已畫了出來的東西<br />\n<br />\n但如果心中想畫的是一個角色,而不是一個單純的小女孩<br />\n繪畫的精準度不足是個致命傷,會演變成畫崩了角色,是條大罪<br />\n更甚者,甚至畫完之後,其他人根本不知道你在畫誰(懂的人知道你畫錯了,不懂的人覺得你畫得很漂亮)<br />\n<br />\n這個時候回望自已畫出來的東西,覺得自已畫了一件垃圾<br />\n玩顏色,玩效果的過程很開心,但出來的結果不開心<br />\n<br />\n當時在巴哈姆特繪畫區詢問畫師們解決方法<br />\n他們一致叫我先學基本功,然後每張畫的意見都是「先學基本功再來談畫畫」<br />\n因此,我停了繪畫接近一年,直至一年前我找了間畫室學素描,學了半年<br />\n(由於過程中不停叫我畫我不想畫的東西-那些基味很重的古典雕塑<br />\n所以學了半年素描後轉玩油畫,直至現在)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QTbnlRJTwo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_QTbnlRJTwo&d=P%2FHcA6ZC53SiTAtl4%2F4Jg%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=70fe9451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QTbnlRJTwo</a><br />\n現在,我又遇上了兩年前的同一個問題<br />\n打破了蒼之雷霆之後,很想畫一隻電子謠精,但是無辦法把她畫出來<br />\n自由打骨架,盡量畫出來,結果變成了另一個人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/232004_eea5ba713a1bc787926268c76c5fad75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F232004_eea5ba713a1bc787926268c76c5fad75.jpg&h=1ef7680f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/232004_161298b1738dc58ae77e4d329ad0f564.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F232004_161298b1738dc58ae77e4d329ad0f564.jpg&h=6a8bdee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我試著找資料抄考,在抄畫的過程中,錯折感很大<br />\n應該是我打從心底裏抗拒抄畫這回事<br />\n因為怎樣畫都畫不準<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/231905_a017e0caf9119cc47e6729799c0161ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F231905_a017e0caf9119cc47e6729799c0161ba.jpg&h=8039eae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/231913_0f7333832da602ca9287fa2301a0f526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F231913_0f7333832da602ca9287fa2301a0f526.jpg&h=7b7ae281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/231917_d7690d204021b4b275307a8012d643dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F231917_d7690d204021b4b275307a8012d643dd.jpg&h=01846fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果怎樣畫也回到原點<br />\n要不是無視角色設定,隨意畫一隻「有蝴蝶翼的藍色妖精」,而不是蒼藍雷霆的閃蝶<br />\n就是不停抄同一張畫的無限迴環<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/21/231746_6058f3c423bec1d6d6b51f16832b7fb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F231746_6058f3c423bec1d6d6b51f16832b7fb0.jpg&h=3410f316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(大約係GV用劍把閃蝶刺死,來個相愛相殺)<br />\n(劇情中沒可能出現的情景)<br />\n我想讓閃蝶淒厲地死去,但在殺她的前題,是我必須要能夠重新創造她<br />\n無辦法把她畫出來,故事也無從談起<br />\n<br />\n玩具(畫具)很容易買,技術卻是難買的<br />\n目前我敗了一套水筆,混色效果不錯,畫些抽像,概念性的東西效果不錯<br />\n至少翅膀畫得很開心<br />\n<br />\n但是要畫一個女孩,甚至把閃蝶畫出來<br />\n我試了幾張,都只是覺得自已在制造垃圾<br />\n感覺錯折感又要把我打回頭了<br />\n今次和之前不同的是,我沒心機回去打機,甚至是任何遊戲<br />\n我沒有其他地方可以讓我重拾開心,生活無論任何地方都在壓逼我"},{"pid":"f78d39500bc3191dc0f439315b3d9a985e9987b7","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"用水彩混色畫翅膀的感覺很順利,很開心<br />\n但畫完之後回頭望<br />\n<br />\n我在畫誰&hellip;<br />\n她根本不是我想畫的角色"},{"pid":"fdf96947802f6dd7a6ef7dac61316c90ab9068e7","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"當沒有主題,隨意繪畫的時候<br />\n因為沒有標準,所以沒有對錯<br />\n只有相對的審美感<br />\n<br />\n當有主題,角色是固定幾位的時候<br />\n因為有標準,所以只有一種畫法<br />\n畫得不準確的就是錯<br />\n別人不知道和認不出你想畫甚麼"},{"pid":"9a2dfc533b8fb0f43fe251ac23f3223b37a646c8","tid":536245,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"畫畫係咁 要不停畫"},{"pid":"ae515ee7fae77e9b873c341698637c011c23ba35","tid":536245,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3182b7ebafe5933aac84098b4bcff6452fce0f31","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a2dfc533b8fb0f43fe251ac23f3223b37a646c8","tid":536245,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"畫畫係咁 要不停畫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"Geting Over it <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_lGDi1EDts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO_lGDi1EDts&d=P%2FHcA6ZC53SiTAtl4%2F4Jg%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=66be7a43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_lGDi1EDts</a>"},{"pid":"b5df0821b61963788a8bb68bcf9c86f2dbb96f10","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae515ee7fae77e9b873c341698637c011c23ba35","tid":536245,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"26"},{"pid":"45c2e39936f3b86e6db9715823795952d4628b47","tid":536245,"uid":135197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"但係睇完你啲畫都覺得基本功唔太好咁<br />\n我唔太識畫畫<br />\n但係睇都出個骨架怪怪地咁<br />\n可以試下多啲畫唔同姿勢先<br />\n再去創造角色<br />\n加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92c297d84e5e1fe05ed4df8ad3a411ddc706ccd","tid":536245,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3182b7ebafe5933aac84098b4bcff6452fce0f31","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a2dfc533b8fb0f43fe251ac23f3223b37a646c8","tid":536245,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"畫畫係咁 要不停畫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"Geting Over it <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_lGDi1EDts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO_lGDi1EDts&d=P%2FHcA6ZC53SiTAtl4%2F4Jg%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=66be7a43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O_lGDi1EDts</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"我都好差 一直畫 試過畫足10個錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好放棄！"},{"pid":"12c834bfa9e14096b5cd2bfbc6cba8f6696437a8","tid":536245,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"點解要打書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e64df26f0f93d799bfb66bc4f55b3c83df2d67","tid":536245,"uid":75427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"呢類型嘅畫就算冇天份都可以畫到，肯努力就可以畫得似架啦!!<br />\n加油啦!!!"},{"pid":"b4fa6cc742e349631844edbd05dc96c8fdac7d18","tid":536245,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffaa33a23f388b0b6f6df647ee9120200b6f98d6","tid":536245,"uid":110770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"學下素描先，我見你連基本比例都錯，骨架又唔match，點會畫得似<br />\n其實好多大師佢地都係靠努力，網上好多系列係show返十年前後之間嘅功力變化，你就會明咩叫熟能生巧<br />\n<br />\n我睇你個人好藝術家性格，腳踏實地少少去練下畫畫"},{"pid":"bea83ce28b55b2018075dbc63e960ac20e36b0f9","tid":536245,"uid":110770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"同埋用鉛筆畫得好先好去掂咩水彩，救命，見到你咁急功近利"},{"pid":"41148daa65e133360c8f337dbd68a06b906a352a","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"bea83ce28b55b2018075dbc63e960ac20e36b0f9","tid":536245,"uid":110770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"同埋用鉛筆畫得好先好去掂咩水彩，救命，見到你咁急功近利"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"點解所有人都話要由素描學起<br />\n<br />\n我試過由素描開始學<br />\n畫左好耐基佬雕塑，骷髏頭<br />\n好似返工咁捱<br />\n又要比錢，又唔開心<br />\n完全係囉苦黎辛<br />\n直至某日夾硬畫張女人床照先有返小小起色<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我逼自已學素描<br />\n係我練成之前已經把自已逼跑了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我認我有Ｄ急功近利<br />\n但如果見唔到目標，我唔相信我會行到去目標<br />\n特別條路要我行去一個相反的方向"},{"pid":"dd39bc0f1987c309b42fb57187bb8cf56944c451","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"12c834bfa9e14096b5cd2bfbc6cba8f6696437a8","tid":536245,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"點解要打書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"係巴哈姆特留連得多"},{"pid":"3aca6f9c5603efc6695ed38323d24594c63ff7a5","tid":536245,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得我可以幫你，我都係最近先摸到個學習方法"},{"pid":"6c9f13526f8fd7d585d884696b675d1f4a8c820e","tid":536245,"uid":157304,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"41148daa65e133360c8f337dbd68a06b906a352a","tid":536245,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"bea83ce28b55b2018075dbc63e960ac20e36b0f9","tid":536245,"uid":110770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"同埋用鉛筆畫得好先好去掂咩水彩，救命，見到你咁急功近利"},"citedB